en_5390178_0	The charge sheet pertaining to the assassination of Bharatha Lakshman Premachandra was handed over to the defendants of the case at the Colombo Magistrate’s Court on Tuesday.
en_5390178_1	Thirteen persons including Parliamentarian R. Duminda Silva have been named as defendants in the case.
en_5390178_2	Accordingly, the charge sheet states that the defendants are responsible for the killing of four persons including Bharatha Lakshman Premachandra, and illegal assembly.
en_5390178_3	Additional Magistrate Priyantha Liyanage questioned the defendants whether they were prepared to provide evidence in this regard.
en_5390178_4	The lawyers representing the defendants informed courts that evidence would be provided by the defendants if the case is referred to the High Court.
